race.description: Yarragon Country Style Bakery Maiden Plate
race.comment: WARRIOR WITHIN (5) resumes and two back went close at Pakenham. Placed in his latest Cranbourne jumpout and Stackhouse rides from the inside barrier. Tough to beat. IGOTMYMINDONYOU (2) missed the frame last start by just 1.2L over 1100m at Traralgon, after being prominent at the turn. Went just as good here prior and fourth up is ready to win. IMMORTALISED (7) was beaten less than 2L at Mornington first-up but was plain after. He's been freshened and jumped out well. He can feature with average luck in the run. CANBECOSTLY (1) has not raced since a 3-length defeat at over 1209m at Yarra Valley on debut. Has had two jumpouts with race-rider Noonan aboard. Will be naturally improved and has shown enough to suggest he can get off the mark.
